  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/TelephonyMessagingKit\/RCSService\/Business\/Card\/Media\/displayHeight\ncrawled: 2025-12-13T03:45:10Z\n---\n\n# displayHeight\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nThe display height for media.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet displayHeight: RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height\n```\n\n## Accessing card media properties\n\n- **url**: URL of media.\n- **contentType**: Content type of media.\n- **fileSize**: File size of media.\n- **thumbnailURL**: URL of thumbnail.\n- **thumbnailContentType**: Content type of thumbnail.\n- **thumbnailFileSize**: File size of thumbnail.\n- **RCSService.Business.Card.Media.Height**: Enumeration indicating the height of the media.\n- **description**: Description of media.\n\n",
